Lár DMN: A Showcase of Cognitive Architectures
Copyright 2025 Aadithya Vishnu Sajeev & Vinay S

This product includes software developed by Snath.ai.

This repository is a specialized showcase of cognitive architectures, demonstrating concepts such as:
- Bicameral Memory Systems
- Autopoietic (Self-Creating) AI
- Neuro-Mimetic Design Pattern (Thalamus/Amygdala/Hippocampus/DMN)

It is built upon the Lár Engine foundation but serves distinct educational and demonstrative purposes.